{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "9b2e1d3a-7c4d-4f0e-9a5b-1f2c3d4e5f60",
    "name": "Tabungan Haji API",
    "description": "Collection untuk Tabungan Haji API (Express 5 + Prisma + PostgreSQL). Base URL & ID-ID pakai variable collection — bisa di-override lewat environment.\n\n**Urutan run yang disarankan (folder demi folder):**\n1. Health Check\n2. Nasabah → Create (akan auto-set `nasabahId`)\n3. User → Create (akan auto-set `userId` + simpan kredensial) lalu Login (akan auto-set `token` JWT)\n4. Tabungan → Create (akan auto-set `tabunganId`)\n5. Transaksi → Create Setoran / Penarikan (akan auto-set `transaksiId`)\n6. Negative Cases (opsional)\n\n**Catatan tipe BigInt:** field `saldo` (Tabungan) dan `nominal`/`saldoSebelum`/`saldoSesudah` (Transaksi) dikirim sebagai **string** di response JSON karena BigInt tidak native ke JSON.\n\n**Autentikasi (JWT):** Collection memakai Bearer Token `{{token}}` di level collection. Endpoint publik (Health, Login, Create Nasabah, Create User) di-set `No Auth`. Sisanya wajib JWT — jalankan **Login** dulu agar `token` tersimpan otomatis. Token berisi data user + `nasabah` sebagai child, berlaku 1 jam. **Logout** me-revoke token di server.",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "auth": {
    "type": "bearer",
    "bearer": [
      { "key": "token", "value": "{{token}}", "type": "string" }
    ]
  },
  "variable": [
    { "key": "baseUrl", "value": "http://localhost:3000", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "nasabahId", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "tabunganId", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "transaksiId", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "userId", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "userUsername", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "userPassword", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "token", "value": "", "type": "string" }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Health Check",
      "request": {
        "auth": { "type": "noauth" },
        "method": "GET",
        "header": [],
        "url": {
          "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/health",
          "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
          "path": ["health"]
        }
      },
      "event": [
        {
          "listen": "test",
          "script": {
            "type": "text/javascript",
            "exec": [
              "pm.test('Status 200', () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));",
              "pm.test('Body has status=ok', () => {",
              "    const j = pm.response.json();",
              "    pm.expect(j.status).to.eql('ok');",
              "});"
            ]
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
