    {
      "name": "User",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Create User",
          "request": {
            "auth": { "type": "noauth" },
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"nasabahId\": \"{{nasabahId}}\",\n  \"username\": \"{{userUsername}}\",\n  \"password\": \"{{userPassword}}\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/user",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "user"]
            },
            "description": "Buat akun login untuk seorang nasabah. Password di-hash (bcrypt) sebelum disimpan dan TIDAK pernah dikembalikan di response.\n\n**Body fields:**\n- `nasabahId` (UUID, wajib) — referensi nasabah, unik (1 akun per nasabah)\n- `username` (string 4-70, huruf/angka/`._-`, wajib, unik)\n- `password` (string 8-72, wajib)\n\n**Status codes:** 201 created • 400 validasi • 409 username/nasabah_id duplikat • 422 NASABAH_NOT_FOUND (nasabahId tidak ada).\n\nPre-request script meng-generate username acak agar bisa di-run berulang, dan menyimpan kredensial ke variable `userUsername`/`userPassword` untuk dipakai request Login."
          },
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "prerequest",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "if (!pm.collectionVariables.get('userUsername')) {",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set('userUsername', 'andhini_' + Math.floor(Math.random() * 100000));",
                  "}",
                  "if (!pm.collectionVariables.get('userPassword')) {",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set('userPassword', 'rahasia123');",
                  "}"
                ]
              }
            },
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('Status 201', () => pm.response.to.have.status(201));",
                  "const j = pm.response.json();",
                  "pm.test('Response punya data.id', () => {",
                  "    pm.expect(j).to.have.property('data');",
                  "    pm.expect(j.data).to.have.property('id');",
                  "});",
                  "pm.test('Password tidak dikembalikan', () => {",
                  "    pm.expect(j.data).to.not.have.property('password');",
                  "});",
                  "if (j && j.data && j.data.id) {",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set('userId', j.data.id);",
                  "    console.log('userId tersimpan:', j.data.id);",
                  "}"
                ]
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "Login",
          "request": {
            "auth": { "type": "noauth" },
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"username\": \"{{userUsername}}\",\n  \"password\": \"{{userPassword}}\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/user/login",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "user", "login"]
            },
            "description": "Validasi kredensial login & terbitkan JWT. Password dicocokkan dengan hash via bcrypt. Sukses 200 mengembalikan `token` (JWT berisi data user + `nasabah` sebagai child) dan `data` user (tanpa password). Test script menyimpan token ke variable `token` untuk dipakai semua request yang butuh JWT. Gagal 401 INVALID_CREDENTIALS untuk username tidak ada maupun password salah (anti user-enumeration)."
          },
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('Status 200', () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));",
                  "const j = pm.response.json();",
                  "pm.test('Login berhasil & dapat token', () => {",
                  "    pm.expect(j.message).to.eql('Login berhasil');",
                  "    pm.expect(j.token).to.be.a('string');",
                  "    pm.expect(j.data).to.not.have.property('password');",
                  "});",
                  "pm.test('Response bawa data nasabah (child)', () => {",
                  "    pm.expect(j.data).to.have.property('nasabah');",
                  "});",
                  "if (j && j.token) {",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set('token', j.token);",
                  "    console.log('token JWT tersimpan');",
                  "}"
                ]
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "List User",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/user",
